.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH btctax-reconcile-pseudo-approve 1  btctax "btctax manual"
.SH NAME
approve \- Promote pseudo default decisions to REAL (attested) decisions in bulk. Shows a preview + requires `\-\-yes` (or `\-\-dry\-run` to preview only). Optional filters restrict which defaults are approved
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBapprove\fR [\fB\-\-kind\fR] [\fB\-\-wallet\fR] [\fB\-\-year\fR] [\fB\-\-dry\-run\fR] [\fB\-\-yes\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Promote pseudo default decisions to REAL (attested) decisions in bulk. Shows a preview + requires `\-\-yes` (or `\-\-dry\-run` to preview only). Optional filters restrict which defaults are approved
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-kind\fR \fI<KIND>\fR
Only approve defaults of this TYPE: `self\-transfer` (unknown\-basis inbound → $0 self\-transfer), `raw` (unclassified row placeholder), or `conflict` (import conflict accept\-first). Omit = all
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
self\-transfer: Unknown\-basis inbound defaulted to a $0\-basis self\-transfer\-in
.IP \(bu 2
raw: Unclassified row defaulted to a zero\-value placeholder (ClassifyRaw)
.IP \(bu 2
conflict: Import conflict defaulted to accept\-first (SupersedeImport)
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-wallet\fR \fI<WALLET>\fR
Only approve defaults whose target event is in this wallet (e.g. `exchange:coinbase:main`)
.TP
\fB\-\-year\fR \fI<YEAR>\fR
Only approve defaults whose target event falls in this tax year
.TP
\fB\-\-dry\-run\fR
Print the preview and exit without writing
.TP
\fB\-\-yes\fR
Skip the interactive confirmation (non\-interactive apply)
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
